' =========================================================
' ハイブリッドアプリ(Ionic + Capacitor)アーキテクチャ
' =========================================================
' レイヤー構造は Android 公式「推奨アーキテクチャ」準拠
'   https://developer.android.com/topic/architecture?hl=ja
'   UI Layer / Domain Layer(Optional) / Data Layer
'   単方向データフロー(UDF)+ Single Source of Truth(SSOT)
'   Data Layer から Capacitor Bridge を介して Native Plugin 経由で SDK に到達
' =========================================================
' 収録ダイアグラム:
'   1. hybrid_layer_structure       レイヤ構造(UI / Domain / Data + Bridge)
'   2. hybrid_udf                   単方向データフロー(UDF)
'   3. hybrid_request_flow          リクエストフロー(カメラアクセス)
'   4. hybrid_plugin_architecture   Capacitor Plugin アーキテクチャ
'   5. hybrid_ht_scanner            HT バーコードスキャナ連携
'   6. hybrid_update_distribution   更新・配信フロー(Live Update 含む)
'   7. hybrid_hw_capability         HW 機能対応
'   8. hybrid_build_pipeline        ビルドパイプライン
' =========================================================

@startuml 1_hybrid_layer_structure

title 【① ハイブリッド(Ionic + Capacitor)】 レイヤ構造\n(Android 推奨アーキテクチャ準拠、Bridge でネイティブへ到達)

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor<<ui>> #FFE0B2
  BackgroundColor<<domain>> #FFCCBC
  BackgroundColor<<data>> #D7CCC8
  BackgroundColor<<bridge>> #FFCC80
  BackgroundColor<<platform>> #BCAAA4
  BackgroundColor<<external>> #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #E65100
}
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor #666
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #666
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #666
}

package "UI Layer (WebView 内、TS)" as UI <<ui>> {
  component "UI Elements\n- Ionic UI コンポーネント\n  (Ion-Button / Ion-Card / Ion-Nav)\n- Angular / React / Vue Component" as UI_ELEMENTS
  component "State Holders\n- Angular Service + RxJS\n- React Context / Zustand\n- Vue Pinia" as UI_STATE
  UI_ELEMENTS -down-> UI_STATE : observes state\nsends events
}

package "Domain Layer (Optional、TS)" as DOMAIN <<domain>> {
  component "UseCases / Interactors\n- 純 TS、プラットフォーム非依存\n- 例: `GetBarcodeHistoryUseCase`\n- 複雑な業務ロジックを切り出し" as USECASE
}

package "Data Layer (TS、Bridge を介してネイティブへ)" as DATA <<data>> {
  component "Repositories\n- SSOT 提供\n- `BarcodeRepository` 等\n- 複数 DataSource の統合" as REPO

  package "Data Sources" as DS {
    component "Remote DataSource\n(fetch / axios)" as DS_REMOTE
    component "WebView Local DataSource\n(IndexedDB / LocalStorage)" as DS_LOCAL_WEB
    component "Native-backed DataSources\n(下記 Bridge 経由)" as DS_NATIVE
  }

  REPO -down-> DS_REMOTE
  REPO -down-> DS_LOCAL_WEB
  REPO -down-> DS_NATIVE
}

package "Capacitor Bridge (JS ↔ Native、非同期 IPC)" as BRIDGE <<bridge>> {
  component "JS 側 Bridge\n(window.Capacitor)\nPromise API" as BR_JS
  component "Native 側 Bridge\n(BridgeWebViewClient)" as BR_NATIVE
  BR_JS -right-> BR_NATIVE : JSON メッセージ
}

package "Plugin 層 (Kotlin / Swift)" as PLUGINS <<platform>> {
  component "公式 Plugin\n@capacitor/camera\n@capacitor/geolocation\n@capacitor/filesystem\n@capacitor/push-notifications" as PL_OFF
  component "Community / Capawesome\n@capacitor-community/sqlite\n@capacitor-community/bluetooth-le\n@capawesome-team/capacitor-nfc" as PL_COMM
  component "カスタム Plugin\n(社内独自実装\nDataWedge Intent BroadcastReceiver 等)" as PL_CUSTOM
}

package "Platform Runtime" as PLATFORM <<platform>> {
  component "MainActivity(Kotlin/Java)" as MAIN
  component "WebView (Android System WebView / WKWebView iOS)" as WV
}

package "External" as EXT <<external>> {
  cloud "API Server\n/ Play / MDM / Appflow OTA" as API
  database "SQLite (Plugin)\nEncrypted Prefs\nAndroid Keystore" as DB
  component "Android / iOS SDK\n(CameraX / BT / NFC / USB /\nWorkManager / Keystore 等)" as SDK
}

UI_STATE -down-> USECASE : calls
USECASE -down-> REPO : uses
UI_ELEMENTS .down.> WV : 実行

DS_REMOTE -down-> API : HTTPS(WebView fetch)
DS_LOCAL_WEB -down-> WV
DS_NATIVE -down-> BR_JS
BR_NATIVE -down-> PL_OFF
BR_NATIVE -down-> PL_COMM
BR_NATIVE -down-> PL_CUSTOM
PL_OFF -down-> SDK
PL_COMM -down-> SDK
PL_CUSTOM -down-> SDK
SDK -down-> DB

MAIN -right-> WV : 起動 + index.html ロード

note right of DATA
  **Data Layer の Data Source 層で**
  **Web API 由来 / Native 由来の両方**を扱う。
  Web-only の Repository は
  PWA とほぼ同じ実装で可
end note

note right of BRIDGE
  **Capacitor Bridge**
  - Promise ベース非同期 IPC
  - 型定義は @capacitor/core
  - Web と Native の境界
  - 同期呼出は不可
end note

note right of PL_CUSTOM
  **HT 案件の DataWedge Intent 受信**
  はこの Plugin 層で実装
  Kotlin の BroadcastReceiver を登録し
  notifyListeners() で WebView へ伝達
end note

@enduml

' =========================================================

@startuml 2_hybrid_udf

title 【②】 単方向データフロー(UDF)+ SSOT\n(WebView ↔ Bridge ↔ Native SDK)

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"

actor User

package "UI Layer (TS)" as UI {
  component "Ionic Component" as COMP
  component "State Holder\n(Pinia / Context / RxJS)" as SH
}

package "Domain Layer" as DOMAIN {
  component "UseCase(TS)" as UC
}

package "Data Layer (TS)" as DATA {
  component "Repository" as REPO
}

package "Bridge" as BRIDGE {
  component "Capacitor Bridge" as BR
}

package "Native Plugin (Kotlin)" as PL {
  component "Plugin" as PLUGIN
  database "SQLite / SDK API" as SDK
  cloud "Remote API" as API
}

User --> COMP : 操作
COMP --> SH : emit event
SH --> UC : invoke
UC --> REPO : fetch / update
REPO --> BR : Capacitor.call()
BR --> PLUGIN : JSON IPC
PLUGIN --> SDK : Room / HW API
PLUGIN --> API : HTTP (一部 Plugin で)
SDK -[#green]-> PLUGIN : Flow / callback
PLUGIN -[#green]-> BR : Promise resolve / event
BR -[#green]-> REPO : Promise / Listener
REPO -[#green]-> UC : Observable
UC -[#green]-> SH
SH -[#green]-> COMP : 再レンダリング

note right of SDK
  **SSOT**
  SQLite(Plugin 経由で Native 管理)を
  信頼点に。Android 側 Room の
  オフラインファースト設計と同じ
end note

note left of BR
  非同期 IPC なので
  高頻度呼出(10ms 刻み等)は不向き
end note

legend right
  | 方向 | 意味 |
  |<color:black>━━━▶</color>| Event(User → 下方) |
  |<color:green>━━━▶</color>| State / Result |
endlegend

@enduml

' =========================================================

@startuml 3_hybrid_request_flow

title 【③ ハイブリッド】 カメラアクセス リクエストフロー

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"

actor User
participant "ネイティブ App\n(MainActivity)" as Native
participant "WebView" as WV
participant "App Logic\n(TS)" as App
participant "Capacitor Bridge\n(JS 側)" as BridgeJS
participant "Capacitor Bridge\n(Kotlin 側)" as BridgeNative
participant "@capacitor/camera\n(Plugin, Kotlin)" as Plugin
participant "Android SDK\nCameraX" as Camera
participant "OS 権限" as OS

User -> Native: APK 起動
Native -> WV: index.html ロード
WV -> App: ページレンダリング
User -> App: 撮影ボタン押下
App -> BridgeJS: Camera.getPhoto({ source: CAMERA })
BridgeJS -> BridgeNative: JSON IPC\n{ "pluginId":"Camera", "methodName":"getPhoto" }
BridgeNative -> Plugin: メソッド呼出
Plugin -> OS: 権限確認 (ActivityResultContracts)
OS -> User: Android 権限ダイアログ
User -> OS: 許可
OS --> Plugin: 許可
Plugin -> Camera: ImageCapture
Camera --> Plugin: ImageProxy
Plugin -> Plugin: Base64 / ファイルパス生成
Plugin --> BridgeNative: 結果オブジェクト
BridgeNative --> BridgeJS: JSON で返却
BridgeJS --> App: Promise resolve
App -> WV: 画像表示

note right of BridgeNative
  Bridge は **非同期 IPC**
  同期呼出はなく、
  全て Promise で返る
end note

@enduml

' =========================================================

@startuml 4_hybrid_plugin_architecture

title 【④ ハイブリッド】 Capacitor Plugin アーキテクチャ

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"

package "JS/TS 側(WebView 内)" as JS_SIDE {
  [Plugin API\n(definitions.ts)] as JS_API
  [TypeScript 型定義] as JS_TYPES
  [registerPlugin\n<\"PluginName\">] as JS_REGISTER
}

package "Native 側(Android Kotlin)" as ANDROID_SIDE {
  [CapacitorPlugin\nアノテーション] as AND_ANNOT
  [Plugin Class\n(extends Plugin)] as AND_CLASS
  [@PluginMethod\n関数] as AND_METHOD
  [Android SDK API] as AND_SDK
}

package "Native 側(iOS Swift)" as IOS_SIDE {
  [CAP_PLUGIN マクロ] as IOS_MACRO
  [Plugin Class\n(: CAPPlugin)] as IOS_CLASS
  [@objc func] as IOS_METHOD
  [iOS SDK API] as IOS_SDK
}

JS_REGISTER --> AND_CLASS : Android 実行時\nroute
JS_REGISTER --> IOS_CLASS : iOS 実行時\nroute
JS_API --> JS_REGISTER
AND_CLASS --> AND_METHOD
AND_METHOD --> AND_SDK
IOS_CLASS --> IOS_METHOD
IOS_METHOD --> IOS_SDK

note bottom of JS_SIDE
  Web 開発者向けの
  フラットな Promise API
end note

note bottom of ANDROID_SIDE
  Kotlin で
  ネイティブ SDK を直接叩く
  (例: CameraX、WorkManager)
end note

note bottom of IOS_SIDE
  Swift で
  iOS SDK を直接叩く
  (例: AVFoundation、CoreBluetooth)
end note

@enduml

' =========================================================

@startuml 5_hybrid_ht_scanner

title 【⑤ ハイブリッド】 HT バーコードスキャナ連携(Capacitor Plugin 経由)

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"

participant "Zebra HT\nスキャナ HW" as HW
participant "DataWedge\nService" as DW
participant "Android Broadcast" as BC
participant "カスタム Plugin\n(Kotlin BroadcastReceiver)" as RECEIVER
participant "Capacitor Bridge" as BRIDGE
participant "WebView /\nApp(TS)" as APP
actor User

== Intent Output モード(カスタム Plugin で対応可能)==
note over RECEIVER #FFF3E0
  Capacitor 公式 Plugin ではないため
  **社内でカスタム Plugin を作成する**のが一般
  または Darryn Campbell 氏のサンプル活用
end note

HW -> DW: トリガーキー → スキャン
DW -> BC: Intent 発行\n(com.symbol.datawedge.api.RESULT_ACTION)
BC -> RECEIVER: onReceive(intent)
RECEIVER -> RECEIVER: getStringExtra("com.symbol.datawedge.data_string")
RECEIVER -> BRIDGE: notifyListeners("barcodeScanned", data)
BRIDGE -> APP: Capacitor イベント発火
APP -> User: 画面反映

== Keyboard Wedge モード(実装不要) ==
HW -> DW: スキャン
DW -> DW: キー入力として OS へ送出
DW -> APP: <input> にフォーカスがあればそのまま文字列が届く
APP -> User: 画面反映(最短)

note right of RECEIVER
  カスタム Plugin で
  実装する Kotlin コード例:
  ----
  @CapacitorPlugin(name = "DataWedge")
  class DataWedgePlugin : Plugin() {
    override fun load() {
      val filter = IntentFilter("com.symbol...")
      context.registerReceiver(receiver, filter)
    }
    private val receiver = object : BroadcastReceiver() {
      override fun onReceive(ctx, intent) {
        val data = intent.getStringExtra(...)
        notifyListeners("scan", JSObject().put("data", data))
      }
    }
  }
end note

@enduml

' =========================================================

@startuml 6_hybrid_update_distribution

title 【⑥ ハイブリッド】 更新・配信フロー(ネイティブ + Live Update)

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"

actor "開発者" as Dev
participant "Git / CI/CD" as CI
participant "Google Play Console /\nMDM / Ionic Appflow" as PLAY
participant "Web アセット CDN\n(Appflow / 自前)" as CDN
participant "端末内 Capacitor\nLive Update Plugin" as LU
actor "ユーザ" as User

== ネイティブ変更あり(プラグイン追加等)==
Dev -> CI: git push (ネイティブコード含む)
CI -> CI: flutter build apk\nor npx cap build android
CI -> CI: AAB 署名
CI -> PLAY: アップロード
note right of PLAY
  ストア審査(Play)
  または MDM 配信
  通常 **数時間〜数日**
end note
PLAY --> User: インストール通知

== Web 資産変更のみ(Live Update)==
Dev -> CI: git push (Web 部分のみ)
CI -> CI: ionic build / npm run build
CI -> CDN: Web アセット配信
note right of CDN #E8F5E9
  **OTA 即反映**
  ストア審査不要
  ロールバックも即可能
end note
CDN --> LU: 新アセット取得(起動時 or 定期)
LU -> User: 次回起動時に反映

note over Dev, User
  Live Update は Ionic Enterprise / Appflow か
  自前実装(@capgo/capacitor-updater 等)で提供
  **Apple/Google ストア規約では「バグ修正・軽微変更」に限定**
end note

@enduml

' =========================================================

@startuml 7_hybrid_hw_capability

title 【⑦ ハイブリッド】 HW 機能対応

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"
skinparam classBorderColor #E65100

class "ハイブリッド(Capacitor)\nの HW アクセス" as HYB <<table>> {
  カメラ               : ◎ @capacitor/camera
  位置情報             : ◎ @capacitor/geolocation
  センサー             : ◎ @capacitor-community/device-motion
  生体認証             : ◎ @aparajita/capacitor-biometric-auth
  --
  BT Classic           : ◎ Plugin
  BLE                  : ◎ @capacitor-community/bluetooth-le
  NFC                  : ◎ @capawesome-team/capacitor-nfc
  USB                  : ◎ カスタム Plugin
  赤外線               : ○ カスタム Plugin(ConsumerIrManager ラップ)
  シリアル(RS-232C)    : ○ カスタム Plugin(USB Serial ラップ)
  UWB                  : △ カスタム Plugin
  Zigbee/Thread/Matter : ○ カスタム Plugin
  UHF RFID             : △ ベンダ SDK を Plugin 化
  --
  DataWedge Wedge      : ◎ <input> 受信
  DataWedge Intent     : ○ カスタム Plugin
  プリンタ(BT/USB)    : ◎ ベンダ SDK を Plugin 化
  プリンタ(ネット)    : ◎ HTTP
  物理キー             : △ WebView 境界で取りこぼし
  --
  HW Keystore          : ◎ Secure Storage Plugin
  長時間 BG 常駐       : △ @capacitor/background-task(制約)
  MDM App Config 注入  : ◎ @capawesome-team/capacitor-managed-configurations
  Device Owner 連携    : ○ カスタム Plugin
  Live Update (OTA)    : ◎ Appflow / @capgo/capacitor-updater
}

note right of HYB
  ◎=公式/安定 Plugin / ○=実装可能だが要カスタム or 品質ばらつき
  △=制約あり / ×=原理的に不可
  **純 PWA で × の多くが、カスタム Plugin で ○ に昇格**
end note

@enduml

